wikipedia_page.main: William Middleton Tennent (6 October 1845 – 5 July 1883) was an English cricketer active in 1867 who played for Lancashire. He was born in Hobart and died in Hastings. He appeared in one first-class match, scoring three runs.

response: William Tennent (1673–1746) was an 18th-century American minister.
